											    <img width="817" height="407" src="https://academiaaeronautica.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/foto_09.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://academiaaeronautica.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/foto_09.jpg 817w, https://academiaaeronautica.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/foto_09-300x149.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 817px) 100vw, 817px" />		                                    			                                    	<span class="nombre-carrera">
		                                    		Piloto comercial de ala fija		                                    	</span>
